snippet.title: Xeno Crisis / Tanglewood - Evercade Cartridge Tour
snippet.description:
Recorded directly off the Evercade VS. In this cartridge, we have two games for Mega Drive. It is also the first post-launch Evercade cartridge.

Games:
00:14 - Tanglewood
09:02 - Xeno Crisis

Tanglewood (C) Big Evil Corp
Xeno Crisis (C) The Bitmap Bureau
